metadata.name: Ancestral Demon - Bael
metadata.description:
Bael is the first Queen of the Underworld and the most powerful of the "Ancestral Demons".
Her army is led by the Demonic Princess - Abaddon.

He mastered the elements of Wind and Fire and instructed his followers in the art of deceit and cunning.

When she learns of the defeat of some of the Demonic Princess by the hands of this young heroine, Erelah, she is intrigued by her powers and her ability to use the Elemental Spirits, No human before Erelah had been able to dominate all 4 and master each Elemental Infusion.

Bael’s aim had become to corrupt Erelah’s soul and make her one of his generals, with demonic powers she would have no rivals.
